For a billionaire power couple enjoying a romantic getaway, Facebook founder Mark Zuckerberg and his wife Priscilla Chan do not exactly look the picture of happiness.

The glum looking pair, pictured while on holiday in Budapest, Hungary, walked with heads down and with less than warm body language.

This month marks a full year since Mr Zuckerberg married his college sweetheart.

