The notoriously down to earth pair wed in May 2012 in Zuckerberg's backyard in Palo Alto, California - after telling their unwitting guests the celebration was solely to mark Chan's graduation from medical school.

The couple sported casual wear on their city break and Mark wore swapped his now-famous sandals, which are parodied by Jesse Eisenberg in the film about Facebook, The Social Network, for a pair of comfortable looking trainers, teamed with a hooded jumper and dark blue jeans.

